      <scopecontent id="aspace_8eefa7fe1e9ba482f9cf9d7fe00353e4">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The Philip Nolan papers document his expeditions from Louisiana into Texas in the years 1791-1801 and the reaction of the Spanish governors of Texas and Nuevo Santander, including the trial of Nolan's men by the Spanish.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
